20.09.2006 SH SCR11799 We can't implemented tests if country or city (noraml and email) is changed, so these test have to be performed always.
If f.e. the country in OCA001 is changed from NL to DE but the city is not changed, then BDH001 claimed about an error of the structure of the city, which is OK. In case of an error CLNT112_ZIP is set to blank. If the country is changed back to NL, so real / new client table have the same value as the temp table for the country field, BDH001 has to be called again because CLNT112_ZIP has to be updated (mandatory field).
